### ============================================================
### BillingController - API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing
### ============================================================

### [1] GET billing dashboard for resident
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/1/dashboard
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### [2] GET billing dashboard - as MANAGER
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/2/dashboard
X-User-Role: MANAGER

###

### [3] GET billing dashboard - resident not found
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/9999/dashboard
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### [4] GET invoices - default pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/1/invoices
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### [5] GET invoices - with pagination params
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/1/invoices?page=0&pageSize=5
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### [6] GET invoices - filter by status OVERDUE
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/1/invoices?status=OVERDUE
X-User-Role: MANAGER

###

### [7] GET invoices - filter by status PAID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/1/invoices?status=PAID&page=0&pageSize=10
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### [8] GET invoices - filter by status PARTIALLY_PAID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/1/invoices?status=PARTIALLY_PAID
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### [9] GET invoice detail
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/invoices/1
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### [10] GET invoice detail - invoice not found
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/invoices/9999
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### [11] GET monthly cost summary
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/1/monthly-cost?fromDate=2026-01-01&toDate=2026-06-30
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### [12] GET monthly cost summary - single month
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/1/monthly-cost?fromDate=2026-07-01&toDate=2026-07-31
X-User-Role: MANAGER

###

### [13] GET payments list - default pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/1/payments
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### [14] GET payments list - with pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/1/payments?page=0&pageSize=5
X-User-Role: MANAGER

###

### [15] GET insurance policies for resident
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/1/insurance-policies
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### [16] GET insurance policies - resident not found
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/9999/insurance-policies
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### [17] POST estimate cost - 30 days
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/1/estimate-cost?estimatedDays=30
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### [18] POST estimate cost - 90 days
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/1/estimate-cost?estimatedDays=90
X-User-Role: MANAGER

###

### [19] POST estimate cost - 1 day
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/2/estimate-cost?estimatedDays=1
X-User-Role: ADMIN

###

### [20] FORBIDDEN - wrong role (NURSE cannot access billing)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/1/dashboard
X-User-Role: NURSE

###

### [21] UNAUTHORIZED - no role header
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/residents/1/dashboard

###
